{"data":{"id":"ChIJ0RCzSxFawokRoImCYFafCDI","rating":4.9,"websiteUri":"https://skydentalnyc.com/?utm_campaign=gmb","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":false,"periods":[{"open":{"day":1,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":1,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":2,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":2,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":3,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":3,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":4,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":4,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":5,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":5,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":6,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":6,"hour":16,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"],"nextOpenTime":"2026-02-17T13:00:00Z"},"userRatingCount":2560,"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJ0RCzSxFawokRoImCYFafCDI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkcFYxTkNWWFJwVm5OaE1ucFhhamhKYURjMVpFRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"4 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I had an amazing experience at Sky Dental! From the moment I walked in, everyone—from the front desk staff to the assistants, hygienist, and doctor—was incredibly warm, welcoming, and professional. I felt genuinely cared for throughout my entire visit. Highly recommend to anyone looking for top-notch dental care in a friendly and comfortable environment!\nAdded note: This is my third time going to Sky Dental. Delighted with their service. Thank you Colleen, Ruth, Christie, Jessi, Lecxy and Dr. T. for making my visit to the dentist more enjoyable.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I had an amazing experience at Sky Dental! From the moment I walked in, everyone—from the front desk staff to the assistants, hygienist, and doctor—was incredibly warm, welcoming, and professional. I felt genuinely cared for throughout my entire visit. Highly recommend to anyone looking for top-notch dental care in a friendly and comfortable environment!\nAdded note: This is my third time going to Sky Dental. Delighted with their service. Thank you Colleen, Ruth, Christie, Jessi, Lecxy and Dr. T. for making my visit to the dentist more enjoyable.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Sarah Aponte","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101978049915539246869/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuV5fSAHt5q0MWNs2GhF524nsYNgPgdl0XD3Pm5jXrZU1JfA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"},"publishTime":"2025-09-29T15:32:24.075766696Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkcFYxTkNWWFJwVm5OaE1ucFhhamhKYURjMVpFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkcFYxTkNWWFJwVm5OaE1ucFhhamhKYURjMVpFRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a114bb310d1:0x32089f56608289a0"},{"name":"places/ChIJ0RCzSxFawokRoImCYFafCDI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSRk0wWkNZM1EwTkdab1VqY3RWbUU0T0dOR1FYYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"4 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"We had a wonderful experience at this dental clinic. Dr. Scott saw my 2-year-old daughter for her very first dental visit, and he was kind, patient, and gentle throughout the appointment. The whole team made us feel comfortable, and my daughter was happy and relaxed. We are very pleased with the care we received and grateful for such a positive first dental experience. Highly recommend","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"We had a wonderful experience at this dental clinic. Dr. Scott saw my 2-year-old daughter for her very first dental visit, and he was kind, patient, and gentle throughout the appointment. The whole team made us feel comfortable, and my daughter was happy and relaxed. We are very pleased with the care we received and grateful for such a positive first dental experience. Highly recommend","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Karina Usmanova","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110049488038558088168/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJW3Z6oXd794JNKTfgUdpawVPNHYyXZyGGPkMZhdjJzDI_HTg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-09-30T12:08:29.345361848Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSRk0wWkNZM1EwTkdab1VqY3RWbUU0T0dOR1FYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSRk0wWkNZM1EwTkdab1VqY3RWbUU0T0dOR1FYYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a114bb310d1:0x32089f56608289a0"},{"name":"places/ChIJ0RCzSxFawokRoImCYFafCDI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2prNGVFWndkSE5uWVU5TllqQkxNMFZmTFY4MGMzYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Really impressed with SkyDental. Danny was kind, gentle, and made sure I was comfortable the whole time—loved the extra comfort touches they offer (Netflix, quiet experience, etc). Camille was so welcoming when I arrived, and Dr. Torkian took her time and really paid attention to detail. She explained my treatment plan thoroughly and helped me understand expected out-of-pocket costs and how to best schedule follow ups. You can tell they genuinely care about their patients. Easily the best dental visit I’ve had. Highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Really impressed with SkyDental. Danny was kind, gentle, and made sure I was comfortable the whole time—loved the extra comfort touches they offer (Netflix, quiet experience, etc). Camille was so welcoming when I arrived, and Dr. Torkian took her time and really paid attention to detail. She explained my treatment plan thoroughly and helped me understand expected out-of-pocket costs and how to best schedule follow ups. You can tell they genuinely care about their patients. Easily the best dental visit I’ve had. Highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Arthur Milhomens","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106101577612967034274/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdJFhc-gzw_E-cmqhvjbNHHND9x5fIr4i4iyK5WKseY4JOwR_E=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-11-08T19:35:44.291585883Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2prNGVFWndkSE5uWVU5TllqQkxNMFZmTFY4MGMzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2prNGVFWndkSE5uWVU5TllqQkxNMFZmTFY4MGMzYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a114bb310d1:0x32089f56608289a0"},{"name":"places/ChIJ0RCzSxFawokRoImCYFafCDI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tobk5UbEpRakV0VDNreU5uaDJZVmxvUlhKS09WRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I really enjoyed my experience at Sky Dental!! Finally switched over after hearing about it from lots of my coworkers who have gone here for years.\n\nStandouts:\n- Lecxy was so patient with me and explained the breakdown of the cost and the transparency is honestly so refreshing.\n- Their front of house staff is efficient, organized, incredibly timely, and still warm. They get you in and out with no frills and there's no doubt that there is an incredible team behind that!!\n- My dentist, Dr. Puzio, is probably the best I've ever had. She's genuine, attentive, and really took her time to make sure I was comfortable and cared for. Went for a second opinion and filling, and her attention to detail/prioritization of my comfort were two aspects that really impressed me.\n- Clean/organized office, has a very family oriented feel to it\n- A 10/10 for their scheduling portal and notification system - was super easy to get an appointment as well as be notified if better times opened up.\n\nOnly downside is that its in FiDi/WTC which is far from where I live/work, but for this quality of care, I'm willing to travel.\n\nWould highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I really enjoyed my experience at Sky Dental!! Finally switched over after hearing about it from lots of my coworkers who have gone here for years.\n\nStandouts:\n- Lecxy was so patient with me and explained the breakdown of the cost and the transparency is honestly so refreshing.\n- Their front of house staff is efficient, organized, incredibly timely, and still warm. They get you in and out with no frills and there's no doubt that there is an incredible team behind that!!\n- My dentist, Dr. Puzio, is probably the best I've ever had. She's genuine, attentive, and really took her time to make sure I was comfortable and cared for. Went for a second opinion and filling, and her attention to detail/prioritization of my comfort were two aspects that really impressed me.\n- Clean/organized office, has a very family oriented feel to it\n- A 10/10 for their scheduling portal and notification system - was super easy to get an appointment as well as be notified if better times opened up.\n\nOnly downside is that its in FiDi/WTC which is far from where I live/work, but for this quality of care, I'm willing to travel.\n\nWould highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Karen Wang","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104940993994177212680/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRjbpLJwJ_bmn29dNqadLDGGVSljDTX05AS1zFwVYUInMfY7mF2Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-10-23T03:39:23.124039789Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tobk5UbEpRakV0VDNreU5uaDJZVmxvUlhKS09WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tobk5UbEpRakV0VDNreU5uaDJZVmxvUlhKS09WRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a114bb310d1:0x32089f56608289a0"},{"name":"places/ChIJ0RCzSxFawokRoImCYFafCDI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMFprdDNRelV5YlhwdFNURTFOSHBNY0Vjd1lYYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"i had a wonderful experience at sky dental. colleen and dr. torkian were extremely kind and non-judgmental, and they handled my dental anxiety with care. i appreciate the transparency with upfront pricing estimates, and the fact that they handle the insurance claims for me. highly recommend!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"i had a wonderful experience at sky dental. colleen and dr. torkian were extremely kind and non-judgmental, and they handled my dental anxiety with care. i appreciate the transparency with upfront pricing estimates, and the fact that they handle the insurance claims for me. highly recommend!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Elliott Shepherd","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109025686957870476673/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2l8aTVPur7aimGyswAQdXVaGdUr6lUXew1_jXpJGvdPd0jkz_=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-12-20T05:58:18.228978285Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMFprdDNRelV5YlhwdFNURTFOSHBNY0Vjd1lYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMFprdDNRelV5YlhwdFNURTFOSHBNY0Vjd1lYYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a114bb310d1:0x32089f56608289a0"}],"photos":[{"name":"places/ChIJ0RCzSxFawokRoImCYFafCDI/photos/ATCDNfVgkV5BI0WYofiQvChUh2Ns9ihJu0JUTcmKcbR1i26zdIgl6DevLdTE4tj6LQTf09MmNPJ3WOJFCeJruW_TqqZvvZfiUbHRAOwQ0rtMzXMZsZ8bokKG-f45ymtqreUL9Zfrv7TkvCpyy5_a_v_NB0wHQ44KsXxmXfZHZf_IAKkH3H6fOPV3NgEID0_E0Q-Uh5jP5OdVDI1kKnertP5e7df1oH097UxS4p8gw4cKG-V6ff3EKn-hoaeOmReKW3vGo86LPZbIiYBKjhkUXgOVThJgEcDvbulkT3R6xNqmb-utoA","widthPx":2731,"heightPx":1536,"authorAttributions":[{"displayName":"Sky Dental","uri":"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/114577107742511219001","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFJlTGVybB6qCJWi25g9ad_uq6o4OQiH6ajsFs15QMWXzP